General.Name: Enad Global 7 AB
General.Description: Enad Global 7 AB (publ) engages in development, marketing, publishing, and distribution of PC, console, and mobile games in Sweden, rest of Europe, North America, South America, Asia, Africa, and Oceania. It operates in two segments, Games and Services. The company also provides consulting services for development strategies and marketing of games; and marketing services. In addition, it releases titles under the Call of Duty, Doom, Diablo, Destiny, and Elden Ring brands. The company was formerly known as Toadman Interactive AB (publ) and changed its name to Enad Global 7 AB (publ) in March 2020. Enad Global 7 AB (publ) was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
